u(x,0)=0
u(x,t)=\sum_{n=1}^\infty B_n \sin \frac{(n\pi ct)}{L} \sin \frac{(n\pi x)}{L}.
B_n=\frac 2{n \pi c} \int_0^L \sin \frac{(n\pi x)}{L} g(x) dx. 
